{"tid":2293292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CCP：香港管得愈緊 白手套功效愈大","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T07:21:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94b7ae0d84b1be32b4ccff216465f9ad2d6fe373","tid":2293292,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"王振民：一國兩制和國安兩者兼融兼得<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部前部長、清華大學法學院教授王振民在一個論壇表示，一國兩制和國家安全是可以兼融和兼得，兩者並不存在衝突，如果國家安全愈牢固，一國兩制的空間就會愈大，亦必須要排除一切外部勢力的干預。<br />\n<br />\n王振民又指，在疫情下本港經濟要謀求出路，應該更積極加入國家的內循環，同時加入國際大循環，兩者不會有衝突。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367125&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=91efdb6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367125</a>"},{"pid":"7e1d4263c69480123126a85df7da06d46ea0704f","tid":2293292,"uid":124382,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"精神分裂最佳病例。"},{"pid":"8bd06b9c301437c55fa7366e2a7752bd763c32f6","tid":2293292,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab51ab7809b9290d405e97a608236e359b23dd71","tid":2293292,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"共產主義源自德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f355482ae47399a50cf3d8202fc31881f5f74a","tid":2293292,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"繼續為你主子畏毒藥喇"},{"pid":"85ffad45632c9189827dcaf546d7624b3c662d08","tid":2293292,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"天氣越寒冷 納dee越強大"},{"pid":"ec27198550cebc907908ec734ed0e6dcb572f